data.name: sqlDataSource1.SelectCommand
data.value: SELECT SchoolCheckedAitiseis.SCHOOL_NAME, SchoolCheckedAitiseis.ΠΛΗΘΟΣ, SchoolTotalAitiseis.ΣΥΝΟΛΟ, ROUND(SchoolCheckedAitiseis.ΠΛΗΘΟΣ * 1.0 / SchoolTotalAitiseis.ΣΥΝΟΛΟ * 1.0, 2) AS ΠΟΣΟΣΤΟ FROM SchoolCheckedAitiseis INNER JOIN SchoolTotalAitiseis ON SchoolCheckedAitiseis.PROKIRIXI_ID = SchoolTotalAitiseis.PROKIRIXI_ID AND SchoolCheckedAitiseis.SCHOOL_NAME = SchoolTotalAitiseis.SCHOOL_NAME ORDER BY SchoolCheckedAitiseis.SCHOOL_NAME
